title: Vox Machina Ep. 16 - Enter Vasselheim
description: The skyship finally touches down in Vasselhein, and Vox Machina set off on their task ahead: Enter the Hall of the Exalt, an ancient vault below the Sanctuary, to lay the Horn of Orcus to its final home. But this task proves much more complex than originally perceived, as the vault is home to a number of nasty tricks and traps...
